Google的储存服务终于姗姗来迟，报导称它将在4月上旬或中旬发布，泄漏的截图显示<a href="http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/news/2012/03/google-drive-leaked-screenshots-show-up-to-5gb-free-storage.ars">它将提供5GB的免费空间</a>。<i>
